    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">🔑</div>
        <h3>Access handled without drama</h3>
        <p>Key fob, lockbox, building manager, tenant coordination — we handle it. You tell us the access method once. Our technician executes without making it your problem to manage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">📋</div>
        <h3>Documentation that holds up</h3>
        <p>Unit number, appliance, failure, repair, parts, technician. Every call. Useful for maintenance logs, owner reporting, habitability documentation, and security deposit records.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">🏢</div>
        <h3>Multi-unit batching</h3>
        <p>Three units with appliance issues in one building? We batch them in a single visit. One truck, shared travel time. You don't pay for three separate trips.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
